## 2. Entity Relationship Diagram (ERD)

The database schema enforces one-to-many relationships where both **Emergency Contacts** and **Incident Logs** are linked to a single registered **User**.

```mermaid
erDiagram
  USER {
    ObjectId _id PK
    string name
    string email UK
    string password
    string phone
    date createdAt
    date updatedAt
  }

  CONTACT {
    ObjectId _id PK
    ObjectId user FK
    string name
    string phone
    string email
    string relationship
    date createdAt
    date updatedAt
  }

  INCIDENT {
    ObjectId _id PK
    ObjectId user FK
    object location "latitude, longitude, address"
    array evidence "fileUrl, fileType, createdAt"
    array locationHistory "latitude, longitude, timestamp"
    string status "active / resolved"
    date resolvedAt
    date createdAt
    date updatedAt
  }

  USER ||--o{ CONTACT : "registers"
  USER ||--o{ INCIDENT : "triggers"
```

